# ArgoCD Conventions

## App of Apps pattern

Root app (`root.yaml`) quản lý tất cả child apps trong `argocd/apps/`.

Current child apps:
| App | Path | Namespace |
|-----|------|-----------|
| puchi-root | argocd/apps | argocd |
| puchi-db | infra/postgres-cluster | puchi-db |
| envoy-gateway-routes | infra/envoy-gateway | envoy-gateway-system |
| puchi-frontend | infra/frontend/web | puchi-frontend |
| puchi-backend-{auth,core,content,grading,user,game,media,notification} | infra/backend/{service} | puchi-backend |

**Không còn Zitadel/Supertokens** — auth-service tự xây dựng thay thế.

## Application spec

```yaml
apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Application
metadata:
  name: puchi-backend-{service}
  namespace: argocd
spec:
  project: puchi
  source:
    repoURL: 'https://github.com/puchidemy/puchi-infra'
    targetRevision: main
    path: infra/backend/{service}
  destination:
    server: 'https://kubernetes.default.svc'
    namespace: puchi-backend
  syncPolicy:
    automated:
      prune: true
      selfHeal: true
    syncOptions:
      - CreateNamespace=true
```

## Project

```yaml
apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: AppProject
metadata:
  name: puchi
  namespace: argocd
spec:
  sourceRepos:
    - 'https://github.com/puchidemy/puchi-infra'
    - 'https://github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend'
    - 'https://gateway.envoyproxy.io/helm'
  destinations:
    - namespace: argocd
    - namespace: puchi-*
    - namespace: envoy-gateway-system
```

- Mỗi component thuộc project `puchi`
- Destination namespace phải nằm trong whitelist của project
- Các source repo phải được khai báo trong `sourceRepos`
- Backend services deploy từ `puchi-infra` repo (image từ GHCR)
